metadata.editComments:
Hi,
My first attempt to analyse a song...
The 4th chord is the best solution I've found, but it's more a Em/A. It could be seen as a V13/ii without the 3rd. But I couldn't find a way to encode this chord.
So bad, You cannot split intro into part 1 / part 2...
First verse should be easier...
